Examples.

|ğ’«ğ’¶ğ“‡ â‰ƒ ğ’«ğ’®eğ“‰| where |ğ’«ğ’¶ğ“‡| is the supercategory of |ğ’®eğ“‰| whose morphisms are partial functions.

