---also known as the |Partial|, |Option|, or |Maybe| monads.
Then, |ğ’«ğ’¶ğ“‡ â‰ƒ ğ’«ğ’®eğ“‰| witnessed by |(A âŸ¶ B) â†’ ( (A + ğŸ™, *) âŸ¶ (B + ğŸ™, *) )|
and conversely |( (A , a) âŸ¶ (B , b) ) â†’ ( A - a âŸ¶ B - b)| where
|X - x â‰¡ Î£ y âˆ¶ X â€¢ Â¬(x â‰¡ y)|.

\begin{spec}
_âŸ¶_ : Set â†’ Set â†’ Set
