%{{{ pointwise
\subsection{Pointwise extensions and the hom functor}
Just as addition can be extended to number-valued functions pointwise |f + g â‰” Î» x â†’ f x + g x|,
we can do the same thing with functors.
\begin{spec}
 -- for bifunctor |_âŠ•_| and functors |F, G| we have a functor |x â†¦ F x âŠ• G x|
