      open Category {{...}}
      compmor : âˆ€ {G H K} {f : G âŸ¶ H} {g : H âŸ¶ K} {x y} {p : x â‡ y} â†’ Functor'.mor' (ğ’«â‚' f â¨¾' ğ’«â‚' g) p â‰¡ Functor'.mor'(ğ’«â‚' (f â¨¾' g)) p
